# Admin 可以订阅系统主题
user admin
topic read $SYS/#

# Admin 可读写S2C主题 Server To Client
user admin
topic readwrite S2C/#
# Admin 可读取C2S主题 Client To Server
user admin
topic read C2S/#

# Users 可读写C2S主题 Client To Server
user users
topic readwrite C2S/#
# Users 可读取S2C主题 Server To Client
user users
topic read S2C/#

#pattern write $SYS/broker/connection/%c/state
